Fragment 函数类型

- Fragment关键属性
  - FragmentManagerImpl mFragmentManager
  - FragmentManagerImpl mChildFragmentManager
  - FragmentHostCallback mHost                 用于回调FragmentActivity中的函数，同时用于获取一些必要资源
  - String mWho = UUID.randomUUID().toString() 每个Fragment创建时都会单独生成该变量，是当前Fragment的唯一标识
  - String mTag;                               Fragment的Tag
  - boolean mRetainInstance;                   用于控制在Activity中持有Fragment的实例，尤其当Activity重建时
  - Fragment mParentFragment;
  - Fragment mTarget;

- 生命周期函数和回调函数

FragmentManagerImpl
  moveToState(Fragment f, int newState, int transit, int transitionStyle,boolean keepActive)

Fragment

  - performAttach() -> onAttach(Context c) -> onAttach(Activity a)
  - performCreate() -> onCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState)
  - performCreateView(...) -> onCreateView(...)
  - f.onViewCreated(f.mView, f.mSavedFragmentState)
  - performActivityCreated() -> onActivityCreated()
  - performStart() -> onStart()
  - performResume() -> onResume()
  - performPause() -> onPause()
  - performStop() -> onStop()
  - performDestroyView() -> onDestroyView()
  - performDestroy() ->  onDestroy()
  - performDetach() -> onDetach()

- 调用Activity(或Context)的函数
   - startActivity()
   - startActivityForResult()
   - startIntentSenderForResult()
   - onActivityResult()
   - requestPermissions()
   - getContext()
   - getActivity()

- 菜单函数
  - setHasOptionsMenu()
  - setMenuVisibility()
  - onCreateOptionsMenu()
  - onPrepareOptionsMenu()
  - onDestroyOptionsMenu()
  - onOptionsItemSelected()
  - onOptionsMenuClosed()
  - onCreateContextMenu()
  - registerForContextMenu()
  - unregisterForContextMenu()
  - onContextItemSelected()

- Fragment状态获取函数
  - isAdded()
  - isDetached()
  - isRemoving()
  - isInLayout()
  - isResumed()
  - isVisible()
  - isHidden()

- Fragment 功能操作函数
  - setShareElement()










































